🎨 Artist: @skyglassinc

//“Dimensional Key” #1//✨sold (link in @VINHWINH bio) DM for inquiries
Hello everybody! 👋 I’m back to work after a little break due to a sliced finger, since I was out of commission and couldn’t work I decided to take a little #DiMensionalTrip... and came back with this little gem. 🤩🙏🌈✨ For me there’s something a bit cathartic about being able to turn what is essentially a pile of broken glass into a symmetrical and completely Uniform piece of glass art: a perfect parallel to what is basically the story of our lives, turning the chaos of our universe and it’s random improbability into what is the beauty of our lives. Life is all a balancing act of everything you take in and you never know how your worst moments can help create your best...The same glass that sliced my finger and kept me from working is what allowed me some time to sit back and reflect on some new ideas... and here are the results of that meditation, hope y’all enjoy 🙏🙏
💎💎💎
SWIPE LEFT for detail shots
This first “Dimensional Key” features one of my most complex and labor intensive designs in a pendant thus far... inspired as a modern take on the #artdeco jewelry aesthetic, this piece features multi-Faceted terraced and stacked layers of my #dimensionalglass tech, all under a #freehandfaceted and polished cut for some crazy angles and optics... This piece comes with a 22” .925 Sterling Silver Chain, be sure to check out the videos above and Swipe Left for a quick glimpse of what Dimensional Shifting feels like! 🤩✨
💎💎💎
This piece and is now #sold online (link in @VINHWINH bio), but feel free to DM for inquiries on making the next one yours! Thank you to all the #VINHWINHcollectors past present and future that share the vision and help make all of this a reality! Every piece I make I am entrusting to y’all to help make sure some of these piece last and are taken care of for future generations to enjoy, my vision of #heirloomglass is in your hands... much love to all who make it happen, happy #DiMensionalTraveling all! 🙏🙌❣️✨
#VINHWINHglass #DimensionalKey #DiMensionalTravelers #artdecocrystal #glassheirloom
